(143, '_transient_dash_a5a61dcab273495c31cd79aafebbdc74', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2017/03/wordpress-4-7-3-security-and-maintenance-release/''>WordPress 4.7.3 Security and Maintenance Release</a> <span class="rss-date">6 Th√°ng Ba, 2017</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.7.3 is now available. This is a security release for all previous versions and we strongly encourage you to update your sites immediately. WordPress versions 4.7.2 and earlier are affected by six¬†security issues: Cross-site scripting (XSS) via¬†media file metadata. ¬†Reported by Chris Andr√® Dale, Yorick Koster,¬†and Simon P. Briggs. Control characters can trick redirect [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wptavern.com/uk-home-secretary-amber-rudd-links-wordpress-com-to-the-spread-of-terrorism''>WPTavern: UK Home Secretary Amber Rudd Links WordPress.com to the Spread of Terrorism</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wptavern.com/wordcamp-miami-2017-will-livestream-all-sessions-this-weekend''>WPTavern: WordCamp Miami 2017 Will Livestream All Sessions this Weekend</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wptavern.com/medium-aims-to-fix-broken-media-with-new-5-subscription-program''>WPTavern: Medium Aims to Fix ‚ÄòBroken‚Äô Media with New $5 Subscription Program</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class="dashboard-news-plugin"><span>G√≥i B·ªï Xung T√≠nh NƒÉng Ph·ªï Bi·∫øn:</span> WooCommerce&nbsp;<a href="plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=woocommerce&amp;_wpnonce=932f4c660f&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800" class="thickbox open-plugin-details-modal" aria-label="C√†i ƒë·∫∑t WooCommerce">(C√†i ƒë·∫∑t)</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
